alpha.com/article/4722681-avepoint-a-solid-saas-data-management-play-benefiting-from-the-ai-revolution\">recommended</a> the shares of AvePoint (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AVPT\" title=\"AvePoint, Inc.\">AVPT</a></span>) in September and things have gone pretty well with the shares up 54%:</p> <p></p> <p>While the shares might have to consolidate recent gains, we continue to think the shares will</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/470621083/image_470621083.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743154-avepoint-keeps-getting-better", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 07:27:51"}, {"id": "4743157", "title": "Rates Spark: CPI Wednesday A Test For Longs", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2078053280/image_2078053280.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"CPI, consumer price index concept. Wooden block with CPI word and stack of coins and increasing graph with shopping cart icon. Goods price inflation and inflation rising. Impact on economic growth\" data-id=\"2078053280\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2078053280/image_2078053280.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2078053280/image_2078053280.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2078053280/image_2078053280.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2078053280/image_2078053280.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2078053280/image_2078053280.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2078053280/image_2078053280.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads