-alex?hasComeFromMpArticle=false&amp;source=content_type%253Areact%257Csection%253Amain_content%257Cbutton%253Abody_link&amp;ticker=KNOP\"><em>earlier articles</em></a> <em>on the company.</em></p> <p>Last week, leading shuttle tanker operator KNOT Offshore Partners LP, or \"KNOP,\" <a href=\"https://www.knotoffshorepartners.com/investors/news/news-details/2024/KNOT-Offshore-Partners-LP-Earnings-Release--Interim-Results-for-the-Period-Ended-September-30-2024/\" rel=\"nofollow\">reported</a></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/185097199/image_185097199.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743148-knot-offshore-partners-stock-q3-no-visible-near-term-catalysts-hold", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 06:13:53"}, {"id": "4743147", "title": "10 Charts That Show The Unprecedented Scale Of The Magnificent 7 Bubble", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/487259374/image_487259374.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Bubble\" data-id=\"487259374\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"4854px\" height=\"3312px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/487259374/image_487259374.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/487259374/image_487259374.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/487259374/image_487259374.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/487259374/image_487259374.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/487259374/image_487259374.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/487259374/image_487259374.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/487259374/image_487259374.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/